{
  "video_id": "_2u_eHHzRto",
  "title": "The era of blind faith in big data must end | Cathy O'Neil",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12795.0,
      "end_time": 14391.0,
      "text": "Algorithms are everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15931.0,
      "end_time": 19550.0,
      "text": "They sort and separate the winners from the losers."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19839.0,
      "end_time": 22102.0,
      "text": "The winners get the job"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22127.0,
      "end_time": 23869.0,
      "text": "or a good credit card offer."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23894.0,
      "end_time": 26544.0,
      "text": "The losers don&#39;t even get an interview"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27410.0,
      "end_time": 29187.0,
      "text": "or they pay more for insurance."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30170.0,
      "end_time": 33566.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re being scored with secret formulas that we don&#39;t understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34495.0,
      "end_time": 37711.0,
      "text": "that often don&#39;t have systems of appeal."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39600.0,
      "end_time": 40356.0,
      "text": "That begs the question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40380.0,
      "end_time": 43293.0,
      "text": "What if the algorithms are wrong?"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 44920.0,
      "end_time": 46960.0,
      "text": "To build an algorithm you need two things:"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46984.0,
      "end_time": 48965.0,
      "text": "you need data, what happened in the past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48989.0,
      "end_time": 50550.0,
      "text": "and a definition of success,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50574.0,
      "end_time": 53310.0,
      "text": "the thing you&#39;re looking for and often hoping for."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53550.0,
      "end_time": 58920.0,
      "text": "You train an algorithm by looking, figuring out."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 58116.0,
      "end_time": 61535.0,
      "text": "The algorithm figures out what is associated with success."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61559.0,
      "end_time": 64210.0,
      "text": "What situation leads to success?"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 64700.0,
      "end_time": 66463.0,
      "text": "Actually, everyone uses algorithms."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66487.0,
      "end_time": 69205.0,
      "text": "They just don&#39;t formalize them in written code."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69229.0,
      "end_time": 70577.0,
      "text": "Let me give you an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70601.0,
      "end_time": 73917.0,
      "text": "I use an algorithm every day to make a meal for my family."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73941.0,
      "end_time": 75417.0,
      "text": "The data I use"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76214.0,
      "end_time": 77873.0,
      "text": "is the ingredients in my kitchen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 77897.0,
      "end_time": 79424.0,
      "text": "the time I have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 79448.0,
      "end_time": 80681.0,
      "text": "the ambition I have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80705.0,
      "end_time": 82414.0,
      "text": "and I curate that data."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 82438.0,
      "end_time": 86689.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t count those little packages of ramen noodles as food."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 86713.0,
      "end_time": 88582.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 88606.0,
      "end_time": 90451.0,
      "text": "My definition of success is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 90475.0,
      "end_time": 93134.0,
      "text": "a meal is successful if my kids eat vegetables."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 94100.0,
      "end_time": 96855.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very different from if my youngest son were in charge."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 96879.0,
      "end_time": 99667.0,
      "text": "He&#39;d say success is if he gets to eat lots of Nutella."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 100999.0,
      "end_time": 103225.0,
      "text": "But I get to choose success."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 103249.0,
      "end_time": 105955.0,
      "text": "I am in charge. My opinion matters."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 105980.0,
      "end_time": 108655.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the first rule of algorithms."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 108679.0,
      "end_time": 111859.0,
      "text": "Algorithms are opinions embedded in code."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 113382.0,
      "end_time": 117450.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s really different from what you think most people think of algorithms."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 117690.0,
      "end_time": 121573.0,
      "text": "They think algorithms are objective and true and scientific."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 122207.0,
      "end_time": 123905.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a marketing trick."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 125890.0,
      "end_time": 127214.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also a marketing trick"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 127238.0,
      "end_time": 130392.0,
      "text": "to intimidate you with algorithms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 130416.0,
      "end_time": 134770.0,
      "text": "to make you trust and fear algorithms"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 134101.0,
      "end_time": 136119.0,
      "text": "because you trust and fear mathematics."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 137387.0,
      "end_time": 142217.0,
      "text": "A lot can go wrong when we put blind faith in big data."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 143504.0,
      "end_time": 146876.0,
      "text": "This is Kiri Soares. She&#39;s a high school principal in Brooklyn."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 146901.0,
      "end_time": 149487.0,
      "text": "In 2011, she told me her teachers were being scored"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 149511.0,
      "end_time": 152238.0,
      "text": "with a complex, secret algorithm"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 152262.0,
      "end_time": 153751.0,
      "text": "called the \"value-added model.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 154325.0,
      "end_time": 157417.0,
      "text": "I told her, \"Well, figure out what the formula is, show it to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 157441.0,
      "end_time": 158982.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to explain it to you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 159600.0,
      "end_time": 161147.0,
      "text": "She said, \"Well, I tried to get the formula,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 161171.0,
      "end_time": 163942.0,
      "text": "but my Department of Education contact told me it was math"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 163967.0,
      "end_time": 165513.0,
      "text": "and I wouldn&#39;t understand it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 167860.0,
      "end_time": 168424.0,
      "text": "It gets worse."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 168448.0,
      "end_time": 171978.0,
      "text": "The New York Post filed a Freedom of Information Act request,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 172200.0,
      "end_time": 174961.0,
      "text": "got all the teachers&#39; names and all their scores"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 174985.0,
      "end_time": 177767.0,
      "text": "and they published them as an act of teacher-shaming."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 178904.0,
      "end_time": 182764.0,
      "text": "When I tried to get the formulas, the source code, through the same means,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 182788.0,
      "end_time": 184937.0,
      "text": "I was told I couldn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 184961.0,
      "end_time": 186197.0,
      "text": "I was denied."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 186221.0,
      "end_time": 187395.0,
      "text": "I later found out"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 187419.0,
      "end_time": 190285.0,
      "text": "that nobody in New York City had access to that formula."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 190309.0,
      "end_time": 191614.0,
      "text": "No one understood it."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 193749.0,
      "end_time": 196972.0,
      "text": "Then someone really smart got involved, Gary Rubinstein."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 196997.0,
      "end_time": 200618.0,
      "text": "He found 665 teachers from that New York Post data"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 200642.0,
      "end_time": 202508.0,
      "text": "that actually had two scores."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 202532.0,
      "end_time": 204413.0,
      "text": "That could happen if they were teaching"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 204437.0,
      "end_time": 206876.0,
      "text": "seventh grade math and eighth grade math."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 206900.0,
      "end_time": 208438.0,
      "text": "He decided to plot them."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 208462.0,
      "end_time": 210454.0,
      "text": "Each dot represents a teacher."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 210924.0,
      "end_time": 213303.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 213327.0,
      "end_time": 214847.0,
      "text": "What is that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 214872.0,
      "end_time": 216149.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 216173.0,
      "end_time": 219619.0,
      "text": "That should never have been used for individual assessment."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 219643.0,
      "end_time": 221569.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s almost a random number generator."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 221593.0,
      "end_time": 224539.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 224563.0,
      "end_time": 225725.0,
      "text": "But it was."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 225749.0,
      "end_time": 226924.0,
      "text": "This is Sarah Wysocki."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 226949.0,
      "end_time": 229124.0,
      "text": "She got fired, along with 205 other teachers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 229148.0,
      "end_time": 231810.0,
      "text": "from the Washington, DC school district,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 231834.0,
      "end_time": 234743.0,
      "text": "even though she had great recommendations from her principal"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 234767.0,
      "end_time": 236195.0,
      "text": "and the parents of her kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 237210.0,
      "end_time": 239242.0,
      "text": "I know what a lot of you guys are thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 239266.0,
      "end_time": 241753.0,
      "text": "especially the data scientists, the AI experts here."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 241777.0,
      "end_time": 246300.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re thinking, \"Well, I would never make an algorithm that inconsistent.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 246673.0,
      "end_time": 248356.0,
      "text": "But algorithms can go wrong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 248380.0,
      "end_time": 252978.0,
      "text": "even have deeply destructive effects with good intentions."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 254351.0,
      "end_time": 256730.0,
      "text": "And whereas an airplane that&#39;s designed badly"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 256754.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258755.00000000003,
      "text": "crashes to the earth and everyone sees it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 258779.0,
      "end_time": 260629.0,
      "text": "an algorithm designed badly"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 262650.0,
      "end_time": 265930.0,
      "text": "can go on for a long time, silently wreaking havoc."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 267568.0,
      "end_time": 269138.0,
      "text": "This is Roger Ailes."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 269162.0,
      "end_time": 271162.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 272344.0,
      "end_time": 274732.0,
      "text": "He founded Fox News in 1996."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 275256.0,
      "end_time": 277837.0,
      "text": "More than 20 women complained about sexual harassment."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 277861.0,
      "end_time": 281960.0,
      "text": "They said they weren&#39;t allowed to succeed at Fox News."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 281120.0,
      "end_time": 283640.0,
      "text": "He was ousted last year, but we&#39;ve seen recently"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 283664.0,
      "end_time": 286334.0,
      "text": "that the problems have persisted."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 287474.0,
      "end_time": 288873.0,
      "text": "That begs the question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 288898.0,
      "end_time": 291782.0,
      "text": "What should Fox News do to turn over another leaf?"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 293650.0,
      "end_time": 296106.0,
      "text": "Well, what if they replaced their hiring process"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 296130.0,
      "end_time": 297784.0,
      "text": "with a machine-learning algorithm?"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 297808.0,
      "end_time": 299403.0,
      "text": "That sounds good, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 299427.0,
      "end_time": 300727.0,
      "text": "Think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 300751.0,
      "end_time": 302856.0,
      "text": "The data, what would the data be?"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 302880.0,
      "end_time": 307827.0,
      "text": "A reasonable choice would be the last 21 years of applications to Fox News."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 307851.0,
      "end_time": 309353.0,
      "text": "Reasonable."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 309377.0,
      "end_time": 311315.0,
      "text": "What about the definition of success?"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 311741.0,
      "end_time": 313650.0,
      "text": "Reasonable choice would be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 313890.0,
      "end_time": 314867.0,
      "text": "well, who is successful at Fox News?"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 314891.0,
      "end_time": 318471.0,
      "text": "I guess someone who, say, stayed there for four years"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 318495.0,
      "end_time": 320149.0,
      "text": "and was promoted at least once."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 320636.0,
      "end_time": 322197.0,
      "text": "Sounds reasonable."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 322221.0,
      "end_time": 324575.0,
      "text": "And then the algorithm would be trained."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 324599.0,
      "end_time": 328476.0,
      "text": "It would be trained to look for people to learn what led to success,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 329390.0,
      "end_time": 333357.0,
      "text": "what kind of applications historically led to success"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 333381.0,
      "end_time": 334674.0,
      "text": "by that definition."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 336200.0,
      "end_time": 337794.0,
      "text": "Now think about what would happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 337819.0,
      "end_time": 340374.0,
      "text": "if we applied that to a current pool of applicants."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 340939.0,
      "end_time": 342568.0,
      "text": "It would filter out women"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 343483.0,
      "end_time": 347413.0,
      "text": "because they do not look like people who were successful in the past."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 351572.0,
      "end_time": 354109.0,
      "text": "Algorithms don&#39;t make things fair"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 354133.0,
      "end_time": 356827.0,
      "text": "if you just blithely, blindly apply algorithms."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 356851.0,
      "end_time": 358333.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t make things fair."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 358357.0,
      "end_time": 360485.0,
      "text": "They repeat our past practices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 360509.0,
      "end_time": 361692.0,
      "text": "our patterns."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 361716.0,
      "end_time": 363655.0,
      "text": "They automate the status quo."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 364538.0,
      "end_time": 366927.0,
      "text": "That would be great if we had a perfect world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 367725.0,
      "end_time": 369370.0,
      "text": "but we don&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 369610.0,
      "end_time": 373162.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ll add that most companies don&#39;t have embarrassing lawsuits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 374266.0,
      "end_time": 376854.0,
      "text": "but the data scientists in those companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 376878.0,
      "end_time": 379670.0,
      "text": "are told to follow the data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 379910.0,
      "end_time": 381234.0,
      "text": "to focus on accuracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 382930.0,
      "end_time": 383474.0,
      "text": "Think about what that means."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 383498.0,
      "end_time": 387525.0,
      "text": "Because we all have bias, it means they could be codifying sexism"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 387549.0,
      "end_time": 389385.0,
      "text": "or any other kind of bigotry."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 391308.0,
      "end_time": 392729.0,
      "text": "Thought experiment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 392753.0,
      "end_time": 394262.0,
      "text": "because I like them:"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 395394.0,
      "end_time": 398369.0,
      "text": "an entirely segregated society --"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 400670.0,
      "end_time": 403395.0,
      "text": "racially segregated, all towns, all neighborhoods"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 403419.0,
      "end_time": 406455.0,
      "text": "and where we send the police only to the minority neighborhoods"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 406480.0,
      "end_time": 407673.0,
      "text": "to look for crime."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 408271.0,
      "end_time": 410490.0,
      "text": "The arrest data would be very biased."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 411671.0,
      "end_time": 414246.0,
      "text": "What if, on top of that, we found the data scientists"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 414270.0,
      "end_time": 418431.0,
      "text": "and paid the data scientists to predict where the next crime would occur?"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 419950.0,
      "end_time": 420582.0,
      "text": "Minority neighborhood."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 421105.0,
      "end_time": 424230.0,
      "text": "Or to predict who the next criminal would be?"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 424708.0,
      "end_time": 426103.0,
      "text": "A minority."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 427769.0,
      "end_time": 431310.0,
      "text": "The data scientists would brag about how great and how accurate"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 431334.0,
      "end_time": 432631.0,
      "text": "their model would be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 432655.0,
      "end_time": 433953.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;d be right."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 435771.0,
      "end_time": 440386.0,
      "text": "Now, reality isn&#39;t that drastic, but we do have severe segregations"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 440410.0,
      "end_time": 441697.0,
      "text": "in many cities and towns,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 441721.0,
      "end_time": 443614.0,
      "text": "and we have plenty of evidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 443638.0,
      "end_time": 446325.0,
      "text": "of biased policing and justice system data."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 447452.0,
      "end_time": 450267.0,
      "text": "And we actually do predict hotspots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 450291.0,
      "end_time": 451820.0,
      "text": "places where crimes will occur."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 452221.0,
      "end_time": 456870.0,
      "text": "And we do predict, in fact, the individual criminality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 456111.0,
      "end_time": 457881.0,
      "text": "the criminality of individuals."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 458792.0,
      "end_time": 462755.0,
      "text": "The news organization ProPublica recently looked into"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 462779.0,
      "end_time": 464803.0,
      "text": "one of those \"recidivism risk\" algorithms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 464827.0,
      "end_time": 465990.0,
      "text": "as they&#39;re called,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 466140.0,
      "end_time": 469208.0,
      "text": "being used in Florida during sentencing by judges."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 470231.0,
      "end_time": 473816.0,
      "text": "Bernard, on the left, the black man, was scored a 10 out of 10."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 474999.0,
      "end_time": 477600.0,
      "text": "Dylan, on the right, 3 out of 10."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 477300.0,
      "end_time": 479530.0,
      "text": "10 out of 10, high risk. 3 out of 10, low risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 480418.0,
      "end_time": 482803.0,
      "text": "They were both brought in for drug possession."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 482827.0,
      "end_time": 483981.0,
      "text": "They both had records,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 484500.0,
      "end_time": 486811.0,
      "text": "but Dylan had a felony"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 486835.0,
      "end_time": 488100.0,
      "text": "but Bernard didn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 489638.0,
      "end_time": 492703.0,
      "text": "This matters, because the higher score you are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 492728.0,
      "end_time": 496201.0,
      "text": "the more likely you&#39;re being given a longer sentence."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 498114.0,
      "end_time": 499407.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s going on?"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 500346.0,
      "end_time": 501678.0,
      "text": "Data laundering."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 502750.0,
      "end_time": 507177.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a process by which technologists hide ugly truths"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 507201.0,
      "end_time": 509220.0,
      "text": "inside black box algorithms"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 509460.0,
      "end_time": 510336.0,
      "text": "and call them objective;"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 511140.0,
      "end_time": 512707.0,
      "text": "call them meritocratic."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 514938.0,
      "end_time": 517323.0,
      "text": "When they&#39;re secret, important and destructive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 517347.0,
      "end_time": 519833.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve coined a term for these algorithms:"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 519857.0,
      "end_time": 521857.0,
      "text": "\"weapons of math destruction.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 521881.0,
      "end_time": 523444.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 523469.00000000006,
      "end_time": 526523.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 526547.0,
      "end_time": 528901.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re everywhere, and it&#39;s not a mistake."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 529515.0,
      "end_time": 533238.0,
      "text": "These are private companies building private algorithms"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 533262.0,
      "end_time": 534654.0,
      "text": "for private ends."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 535340.0,
      "end_time": 538248.0,
      "text": "Even the ones I talked about for teachers and the public police,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 538272.0,
      "end_time": 540141.0,
      "text": "those were built by private companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 540165.0,
      "end_time": 542396.0,
      "text": "and sold to the government institutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 542420.0,
      "end_time": 544293.0,
      "text": "They call it their \"secret sauce\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 544317.0,
      "end_time": 546445.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s why they can&#39;t tell us about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 546469.0,
      "end_time": 548689.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also private power."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 549744.0,
      "end_time": 554439.0,
      "text": "They are profiting for wielding the authority of the inscrutable."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 556934.0,
      "end_time": 559867.0,
      "text": "Now you might think, since all this stuff is private"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 559892.0,
      "end_time": 561500.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s competition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 561740.0,
      "end_time": 563380.0,
      "text": "maybe the free market will solve this problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 563404.0,
      "end_time": 564653.0,
      "text": "It won&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 564677.0,
      "end_time": 567797.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a lot of money to be made in unfairness."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 568947.0,
      "end_time": 572316.0,
      "text": "Also, we&#39;re not economic rational agents."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 572851.0,
      "end_time": 574143.0,
      "text": "We all are biased."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 574780.0,
      "end_time": 578156.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re all racist and bigoted in ways that we wish we weren&#39;t,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 578181.0,
      "end_time": 580200.0,
      "text": "in ways that we don&#39;t even know."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 581172.0,
      "end_time": 584253.0,
      "text": "We know this, though, in aggregate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 584277.0,
      "end_time": 587497.0,
      "text": "because sociologists have consistently demonstrated this"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 587521.0,
      "end_time": 589185.0,
      "text": "with these experiments they build,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 589210.0,
      "end_time": 591778.0,
      "text": "where they send a bunch of applications to jobs out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 591802.0,
      "end_time": 594303.0,
      "text": "equally qualified but some have white-sounding names"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 594327.0,
      "end_time": 596330.0,
      "text": "and some have black-sounding names,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 596570.0,
      "end_time": 598751.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s always disappointing, the results -- always."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 599330.0,
      "end_time": 601101.0,
      "text": "So we are the ones that are biased,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 601125.0,
      "end_time": 604554.0,
      "text": "and we are injecting those biases into the algorithms"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 604578.0,
      "end_time": 606390.0,
      "text": "by choosing what data to collect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 606414.0,
      "end_time": 609157.0,
      "text": "like I chose not to think about ramen noodles --"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 609181.0,
      "end_time": 610806.0,
      "text": "I decided it was irrelevant."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 610830.0,
      "end_time": 616514.0,
      "text": "But by trusting the data that&#39;s actually picking up on past practices"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 616538.0,
      "end_time": 618552.0,
      "text": "and by choosing the definition of success,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 618576.0,
      "end_time": 622559.0,
      "text": "how can we expect the algorithms to emerge unscathed?"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 622583.0,
      "end_time": 624939.0,
      "text": "We can&#39;t. We have to check them."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 625985.0,
      "end_time": 627694.0,
      "text": "We have to check them for fairness."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 627718.0,
      "end_time": 630429.0,
      "text": "The good news is, we can check them for fairness."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 630453.0,
      "end_time": 633805.0,
      "text": "Algorithms can be interrogated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 633829.0,
      "end_time": 635863.0,
      "text": "and they will tell us the truth every time."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 635887.0,
      "end_time": 638380.0,
      "text": "And we can fix them. We can make them better."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 638404.0,
      "end_time": 640779.0,
      "text": "I call this an algorithmic audit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 640803.0,
      "end_time": 642482.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ll walk you through it."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 642506.0,
      "end_time": 644702.0,
      "text": "First, data integrity check."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 645952.0,
      "end_time": 648609.0,
      "text": "For the recidivism risk algorithm I talked about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 649402.0,
      "end_time": 652975.0,
      "text": "a data integrity check would mean we&#39;d have to come to terms with the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 652999.0,
      "end_time": 656525.0,
      "text": "that in the US, whites and blacks smoke pot at the same rate"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 656549.0,
      "end_time": 659340.0,
      "text": "but blacks are far more likely to be arrested --"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 659580.0,
      "end_time": 662242.0,
      "text": "four or five times more likely, depending on the area."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 663137.0,
      "end_time": 665963.0,
      "text": "What is that bias looking like in other crime categories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 665987.0,
      "end_time": 667438.0,
      "text": "and how do we account for it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 667982.0,
      "end_time": 671210.0,
      "text": "Second, we should think about the definition of success,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 671450.0,
      "end_time": 672425.0,
      "text": "audit that."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 672450.0,
      "end_time": 675202.0,
      "text": "Remember -- with the hiring algorithm? We talked about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 675226.0,
      "end_time": 678391.0,
      "text": "Someone who stays for four years and is promoted once?"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 678415.0,
      "end_time": 680184.0,
      "text": "Well, that is a successful employee,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 680208.0,
      "end_time": 683286.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s also an employee that is supported by their culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 683909.0,
      "end_time": 685835.0,
      "text": "That said, also it can be quite biased."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 685859.0,
      "end_time": 687924.0,
      "text": "We need to separate those two things."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 687948.0,
      "end_time": 690374.0,
      "text": "We should look to the blind orchestra audition"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 690398.0,
      "end_time": 691594.0,
      "text": "as an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 691618.0,
      "end_time": 694374.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s where the people auditioning are behind a sheet."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 694766.0,
      "end_time": 696697.0,
      "text": "What I want to think about there"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 696721.0,
      "end_time": 700138.0,
      "text": "is the people who are listening have decided what&#39;s important"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 700162.0,
      "end_time": 702191.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;ve decided what&#39;s not important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 702215.0,
      "end_time": 704274.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re not getting distracted by that."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 704781.0,
      "end_time": 707530.0,
      "text": "When the blind orchestra auditions started,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 707554.0,
      "end_time": 710997.0,
      "text": "the number of women in orchestras went up by a factor of five."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 712730.0,
      "end_time": 714880.0,
      "text": "Next, we have to consider accuracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 715530.0,
      "end_time": 718787.0,
      "text": "This is where the value-added model for teachers would fail immediately."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 719398.0,
      "end_time": 721560.0,
      "text": "No algorithm is perfect, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 722440.0,
      "end_time": 726450.0,
      "text": "so we have to consider the errors of every algorithm."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 726656.0,
      "end_time": 731150.0,
      "text": "How often are there errors, and for whom does this model fail?"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 731670.0,
      "end_time": 733387.0,
      "text": "What is the cost of that failure?"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 734254.0,
      "end_time": 736461.0,
      "text": "And finally, we have to consider"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 737793.0,
      "end_time": 739979.0,
      "text": "the long-term effects of algorithms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 740686.0,
      "end_time": 742893.0,
      "text": "the feedback loops that are engendering."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 743406.0,
      "end_time": 744641.0,
      "text": "That sounds abstract,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 744666.0,
      "end_time": 747330.0,
      "text": "but imagine if Facebook engineers had considered that"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 748900.0,
      "end_time": 752945.0,
      "text": "before they decided to show us only things that our friends had posted."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 753581.0,
      "end_time": 756815.0,
      "text": "I have two more messages, one for the data scientists out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 757270.0,
      "end_time": 760679.0,
      "text": "Data scientists: we should not be the arbiters of truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 761340.0,
      "end_time": 765123.0,
      "text": "We should be translators of ethical discussions that happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 765147.0,
      "end_time": 766441.0,
      "text": "in larger society."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 767399.0,
      "end_time": 769532.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 769556.0,
      "end_time": 771112.0,
      "text": "And the rest of you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 771831.0,
      "end_time": 773227.0,
      "text": "the non-data scientists:"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 773251.0,
      "end_time": 774749.0,
      "text": "this is not a math test."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 775452.0,
      "end_time": 776800.0,
      "text": "This is a political fight."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 778407.0,
      "end_time": 782314.0,
      "text": "We need to demand accountability for our algorithmic overlords."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 783938.0,
      "end_time": 785437.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
